== Description ==

Vice Versa allows you to easily convert WordPress Posts to Pages and Pages to Posts. You can also assign a Page or Post a parent or category(s) as you are converting from one to the other. Vice Versa is easy to install and use. No database tables are affected during installation and there are no additional settings required for the Vice Versa to work.

== Installation ==

*Use the Plugin installer which is located in the WordPress Dashboard menu under "Plugins > Add New". OR ...
*Download Vice Versa.
*Unzip vice-versa.zip. 
*Upload the folder named 'vice-versa' to the wp-content/plugins directory on your server
*Go to the plugins manager in your Wordpress Dashboard and locate Vice Versa in the list of plugins (under 'V' for 'Vice Versa').
*Click Activate.
*Go to my website and make a generous monetary donation.  

Once the plugin is activated, you will find Vice Versa in the Dashboard menu under "Tools".

